    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/b27e0201d64c92ece66e6bdb61e646d5.poster.avif?t=1768843623\" width=480 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/b27e0201d64c92ece66e6bdb61e646d5.webm?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/b27e0201d64c92ece66e6bdb61e646d5.mp4?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一纸合约，丰厚报酬，还有一次前往北极圈神秘远征的机会。机遇诱人，叫人如何拒绝？任务本应简单明了——为一艘代号&quot;北境-3号&quot;的神秘苏联潜艇母舰提供技术支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运却暗中设下陷阱：你主动请缨，替代一位身患重病的机械师执行任务。谁料祸不单行，一切都偏离了原定轨道。此刻的你，被困在这深不见底的海域，在一座早已废弃的苏联研究基地废墟中孤立无援。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/c3348d6bf7326316222b18ff7c15879a.poster.avif?t=1768843623\" width=320 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/c3348d6bf7326316222b18ff7c15879a.webm?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/c3348d6bf7326316222b18ff7c15879a.mp4?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你唯一的生存希望，寄托于掌握这艘尖端潜艇，唯有如此掌握其操作系统，才能揭开这里尘封数十载的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 当心，在这片漆黑的水域中，暗流涌动，你不是唯一的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深海利刃</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/65107bbaaa7dad32b6b617c9bb8f09e6.avif?t=1768843623\" width=616 height=199 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;北境&quot;号潜艇凝聚了那个时代最尖端的科技结晶。时隔数十年，某些设备虽已显露岁月痕迹，但其他装置的先进程度依然令人叹为观止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/367a841430a38e0d76d892762583df0c.poster.avif?t=1768843623\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/367a841430a38e0d76d892762583df0c.webm?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/367a841430a38e0d76d892762583df0c.mp4?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用全息导航系统在禁区迷宫中找寻方向，借助声纳系统洞察周遭环境，操控水下无人机与外界展开互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记得时刻关注能源消耗指标，船载核反应堆极易发生过热危机。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >禁区之域</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/a10df04cb7c20d15b1eb7e9fe39ffdb9.poster.avif?t=1768843623\" width=540 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/a10df04cb7c20d15b1eb7e9fe39ffdb9.webm?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188510/extras/a10df04cb7c20d15b1eb7e9fe39ffdb9.mp4?t=1768843623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入这座建立在异常区域上的研究基地废墟。数十年前，一场离奇的灾难导致整个基地在一夜之间人间蒸发。在探索这片禁忌之域时，抽丝剥茧，揭开历史真相，寻找逃生之机！</p>",
